the magician into a God.

9
00:00:26,619 --> 00:00:28,739
Oh, thank Christ.
I didn't think I'd get through.

10
00:00:28,749 --> 00:00:30,529
Listen, I don't have a lot of time.

11
00:00:30,549 --> 00:00:31,749
We need your help.

12
00:00:31,779 --> 00:00:33,299
