36
00:01:30,245 --> 00:01:31,975
But I am going to have

37
00:01:31,985 --> 00:01:34,935
to momentarily kill you again.

38
00:01:34,945 --> 00:01:36,585
Shh, shh.

39
00:01:36,595 --> 00:01:38,895
[SIGHS]

40
00:01:38,905 --> 00:01:41,725
