230
00:09:51,262 --> 00:09:52,642
I have an idea.

231
00:09:52,652 --> 00:09:55,952
So do all rabbits talk, or...?

232
00:09:55,962 --> 00:09:58,562
Some of them you have
to bribe with cigarettes first.

233
00:09:58,572 --> 00:09:59,771
